Problem statement: Given a number ‘N’, find out the sum of the first N natural numbers.

#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main(){
  int n;
  cin>>n;
  int sum=0;
  for(int i=0;i<=n;i++){
    sum=sum+i;
    
  }
  cout<<"sum is "<<sum;
  
}
Time Complexity: O(N)
Space Complexity: O(1)
